These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-1::.
City: venice, paris
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving
House: craftsman, futuristic
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, tulip
1. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
2. the futuristic house is the person who growstulip##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| City          | paris    | venice |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | skydiving |
| House   | craftsman    | futuristic    |
| Flower   | aconite  | tulip |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, scientist
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, tiparillo
2 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
2. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Job          | bartender | scientist   |
| Cigar   | tiparillo        | fonseca     |
| Pet           | cat         | rabbit     |
| Birthday     | january         | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-3::.
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, pineapple
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, apricot
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, chinese
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
2. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
3. the person who likes apricot is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Food         | pineapple      | lettuce    |
| Color           | purple | apricot |
| Nationality   | chinese       | colombian    |
| Transport     | motorbike    | ship     |

