2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, july
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, aconite
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person who growsaconite##5
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Beverage      | coffee  | 7up        |
| Pet         | bird | chinchilla |
| Birthday   | august    | july    |
| Flower     | aconite | rose        |

